            career where I constantly run into new problems that can only be
            solved by furthering my knowledge and skills. When I'm not working,
            you can find me writing, producing and performing electronic music
            as <a
              href="https://soundcloud.com/food4ghosts"
              target="_blank"
              class="font-spaceMono font-semibold underline underline-offset-2 dark:text-emerald-400 text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-900 hover:dark:text-emerald-100"
